\p
\v 12 Then Shealtiyel's son Zerubavel and Yehotsadak's son Yehoshua, the high priestВҰ375779, and all the rest of the people listenedВҰ375769 to the voiceВҰ375785 of their god Yahweh \add вүҲvia\add* the wordsВҰ375790 of the prophetВҰ375792 HaggaiВҰ375791, because Yahweh their god had sent him, and the people \add вүҲrespected\add* Yahweh.
