\p
\v 1 On the 21st of the seventhВҰ375862 month \add (about a month later)\add*, YahwehВҰ375869 \add вүҲspoke\add* \add again\add* through the prophetВҰ375873 HaggaiВҰ375872:
\v 2 Please \add вүҲask\add* Shealtiyel's son Zerubavel, the governorВҰ375885 of YehudahВҰ375886, and \add вүҲask\add* Yehotsadak's son Yehoshua, the highВҰ375894 priestВҰ375893, and \add вүҲask\add* the rest of the peopleВҰ375898,
\v 3 вҖң\add вүҲAre there any of you still alive who sawВҰ375905 the splendour of the formerВҰ375911 temple\add*? How does it look to you now? \add вүҲIt must now seem pretty much like \em nothingВҰ375919\em* inВҰ375902 comparison\add*.\x + \xo 2:3: \xt Ezr 3:12.\x*
