\v 6 because armyВҰ375974 commanderВҰ375974 YahwehВҰ375973 saysВҰ375972 that in a littleВҰ375977 while, I'llВҰ375979 shakeВҰ375980 the heavensВҰ375983 and the earthВҰ375986, the seaВҰ375989 and the dry land, once more.\x + \xo 2:6: \xt Heb 12:26.\x*
\v 7 I'll shakeВҰ375994 all the nations, andВҰ375994 they'll come \add here bringing\add* their treasure. ThenВҰ375994 I'll fill this \add вүҲtemple\add* with \add my\add* splendourВҰ376010, says armyВҰ376013 commanderВҰ376013 YahwehВҰ376012.
