\v 13 ThenВҰ376108 HaggaiВҰ376109 asked, вҖң\add ButВҰ376108\add* if a person became unclean by touching a corpseВҰ376115 andВҰ376108 thenВҰ376108 touched any of that \add food\add*, would it become unclean?вҖқ\x + \xo 2:13: \xt Num 19:11-22.\x*
