\v 14 вҖң\add вүҲThat's what YahwehВҰ376139 declares about you\add* peopleВҰ376129,вҖқ HaggaiВҰ376126 \add вүҲcontinuedВҰ376125\add*. вҖң\add He says that\add* \add вүҲthat's how this countryВҰ376134 acts towards him\add*. \add вүҲYour actions are dishonourable, andВҰ376125 thenВҰ376125 that same disrespect transfers to your offerings\add*.
